{"ok":true,"concepts":[{"title":"Blush Bloom","description":"A sophisticated cream-frosted chocolate cake adorned with delicate, hand-sculpted sugar roses and peonies in varying shades of soft blush, accented with subtle edible gold dust.","prompt":"A photorealistic, perfectly round 250g, 1-tier luxury chocolate birthday cake, frosted smoothly in cream. It is adorned with exquisite, lifelike hand-sculpted sugar roses and peonies in soft blush, scattered delicately across the top and sides. Subtle edible gold dust highlights the petal edges. Studio lighting, elegant, premium cake studio photography, high resolution.","imageUrl":"data:image/png;base64,"},{"title":"Gilded Arch","description":"A minimalist cream cake featuring a striking, hand-painted blush arch design that sweeps elegantly across one side, highlighted by a delicate edible gold leaf border.","prompt":"A photorealistic, perfectly round 250g, 1-tier luxury chocolate birthday cake, frosted flawlessly in smooth cream. A striking, hand-painted abstract arch design in soft blush elegantly sweeps across one side, outlined with delicate edible gold leaf. Minimalist, modern, elegant birthday cake, premium cake studio photography, sharp focus, high resolution.","imageUrl":"data:image/png;base64,"},{"title":"Whispering Ruffles","description":"A dreamlike creation featuring intricate, wafer-thin cream fondant ruffles cascading around the cake's base, subtly revealing hints of soft blush beneath, crowned with a delicate edible pearl.","prompt":"A photorealistic, perfectly round 250g, 1-tier luxury chocolate birthday cake, encased in ethereal, cascading wafer-thin cream fondant ruffles around its circumference. Hints of soft blush are subtly visible beneath the delicate ruffles. A single delicate edible pearl adorns the top. Elegant, romantic, premium cake studio photography, soft lighting, high resolution.","imageUrl":"data:image/png;base64,"}]}